div.p:
I anſwer, it is very true; for all government and Miniſtry, that is lifted up by Imagination, is to be throwne downe, and plucked up: That Chriſt alone may be exalted in the day of his power. And you have Scripture for it;


Then cometh the end, when he ſhall have delivered up the Kingdome to God, even the Father, when he ſhall have put downe all rule, and all Authoritie, and all power; for he muſt reigne, till he hath put all enemies under his feet, 
                     1 Cor. 15.24.
